    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/63354b14ed3959e987a7c530dbaa7e01.poster.avif?t=1765294305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/63354b14ed3959e987a7c530dbaa7e01.webm?t=1765294305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/63354b14ed3959e987a7c530dbaa7e01.mp4?t=1765294305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《蒸汽朋克神兵》（Steampunk Shinobi）</strong>是一款roguelite动作游戏，它将带您在一个充满活力、不断发展的世界中展开无情的复仇冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >传承驱动的游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每名忍者都由程序生成，每名继承者都具有独特的能力和属性。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的传奇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的珍贵物品送到总部，它们会随着时间的推移得到强化，将普通装备转化为传奇物品。利用新设施扩建你的基地，解锁独特的能力和升级，让每一代都比上一代更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/b17851817e4ca214103487c0acef3328.poster.avif?t=1765294305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/b17851817e4ca214103487c0acef3328.webm?t=1765294305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/b17851817e4ca214103487c0acef3328.mp4?t=1765294305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不断进化的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的选择会影响您的忍者和周围世界的命运，地图和程序化环境会随着您的行动不断进化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战术与激战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为您的忍者配备专用蒸汽武器和精湛的战斗技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/41c05934fe293642660eac8fd6ab2499.poster.avif?t=1765294305\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/41c05934fe293642660eac8fd6ab2499.webm?t=1765294305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284770/extras/41c05934fe293642660eac8fd6ab2499.mp4?t=1765294305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的视觉风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在等距 3D 和像素艺术的绝妙融合中，灵感来自蒸汽朋克美学和中世纪日本。</p>",
